Package venice.lib.networkRSB

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClassMatcher
    Collects reflection classes and methods for matching data holding classes between different protocols.
    NamedPair
    Holds the names of classes and methods for a class-to-class match.
    NamedPairList
    Maintains a list of named pairs for the class matcher.
    RSBHandler
    Waits for new RSB-Events and transfers the received RSB-data to the master-listener (of the application that uses this library).
    RSBNamespaceBuilder
    Takes care of namespace- and slot-creating for the RSB network.
    ValueParser
    Provides methods to convert between strings and protobuf messages.
